      <h3 class="about-font">
        GERTY is a Virtual Personal Assistant that helps you find information quickly. Be it current weather,
        breaking news or to check latest movie review or getting happy with an Giphy images to start your day!
        Ask away and get answer to your question and get on without scrolling through endless pages
        of google search results.
      </h3>
